data.description: Enjoy your pristine and private 3 Bedroom, plus Den, pool and spa home with plenty of room for entertaining on your new expansive Lanai. Enjoy the fresh outdoor air and colorful sunsets, while entertaining poolside with family and friends.  This home is located in the perfect location, close to world class shopping, restaurants, RSW, FGCU, Coconut Point, Miromar Outlets, Gulf Coast Town Center, Red Sox + MN Twins Stadiums and more! This Lilac model offers three separate dwelling wings for privacy and is built to a recent hurricane code, so insurance rates are lower than other areas. With almost 2200 square feet of living space, you will LOVE coming home to your tropical oasis. Features include: Concrete Block Construction, Energy Efficient HVAC, Gourmet Kitchen with Wood Cabinetry, Granite Countertops and Stainless GE Appliances, Plantation Shutters, Volume Ceilings, Dramatic Archways, Large Rooms, Designer Light Fixtures and Fans, Diagonal Tile and Wood Plank Tile, HUGE Walk-In Closets with Loads of Storage, Storm Garage Door, Oversized Screened Lanai, Custom Blinds, No Flood Insurance Needed and more! This is where you want to live. Please call to schedule your appointment today.
